column5: Take a tour around KL City where the city truly is a metropolis with a big central business district with many tall skyscrapers, many international renowned hotels and numerous luxurious shopping malls.
Malacca is famous for its well-preserved historical buildings along with its delicious street foods. Get this pass now to fully enjoy a day tour around Malacca's famous spots!

Being the only place that is able to grow strawberries all year round due to its cooler climate, Cameron Highlands is famous for its strawberry fields. Take this chance to tour around Cameron Highlands and enjoy chilly fresh air!

column6: Take a trip up to Pahang's famous Genting Highlands which is famous for its casinos and theme parks along with its chilly air.
Get a chance to tour around famous Penang's local attractions with our friendly tour guide. Meals and hotel included in package!

Take the weekend off and stay in the city center of Malacca to enjoy its day to night beauty. Get a chance explore the City of Melaka by gliding along Sungai Melaka on a cruise boat and also tour around the tourist sites.
